"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8ad557c363f6864086744d8edda7d02d386ec7","tid":1512603,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:11:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n嗰日玩人鍊呢d咁輕鬆嘅野都有人叫到拆晒"},{"pid":"5767eb0fa3781ce5d67ffdc25f22ece94f56309c","tid":1512603,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:15:50.000Z","msg":"轉做敲節奏work唔work？？？<br />\n例如： 123    123   123   123維持三分鐘抖一抖，等到15分鐘後再黎"},{"pid":"60ec119c19e2ee4ea1cc70f67d88836a061b7ec9","tid":1512603,"uid":230803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444d7b55630947998987b19157352cc4e14601fd","tid":1512603,"uid":300163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好真係9嗌呀屌你</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢派日日落街9嗌，聽到啲手足嗌到把聲沙晒<br />\n我想講，依家係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日日嗌</span></strong></span><br />\n如果唔識得錫住把聲，個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聲帶會好傷</span></strong></span>！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n小弟有做啲啲聲線訓練，唔敢同個啲學opera singing 嘅人比<br />\n但係都可以教到基本嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>發聲</strong></span>、<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">護聲</span></strong>技巧俾大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1。丹田呼吸</span></span></strong><br />\n好啦，見到大家都開post 話丹田呼吸啦<br />\n丹田通常啲人話係肚擠下三個手指位（其實視乎唔同人同學派啦）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">先測試一下你哋平時用咩呼吸方法先！！</span><br />\n各位先坐直，一隻手放向丹田，一隻手放向上胸，然後吸氣<br />\n如果你係上胸姐係漲起先，<br />\n姐係你平時係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">胸口呼吸</span></strong></span><br />\n反之，丹田個隻手漲起，但另一隻手冇漲<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">腹式呼吸</span></span>啦！<br />\n<del>但當然，丹田隻手漲起，再到上胸隻手漲起，又係另一種，學瑜珈太極老師話咁好啲...</del><br />\nAnyway。。。。<br />\n搵到之後，試下得閒就咁做<br />\n吸氣個陣，提自己，丹田個隻手漲起先！要吸氣吸到落丹田！<br />\n仲有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另一個方法</span></strong>，等大家容易啲搵到腹式呼吸<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=784x10000:format=jpg/path/sd5bb08e12f75bcf7/image/i55d1c4e33781ec9b/version/1471595633/semi-supine-or-constructive-rest-in-the-alexander-technique.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.jimcdn.com%2Fapp%2Fcms%2Fimage%2Ftransf%2Fdimension%3D784x10000%3Aformat%3Djpg%2Fpath%2Fsd5bb08e12f75bcf7%2Fimage%2Fi55d1c4e33781ec9b%2Fversion%2F1471595633%2Fsemi-supine-or-constructive-rest-in-the-alexander-technique.jpg&h=2077ee30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖係嚟自Alexander technique 嘅semi supine<br />\n大家試下咁樣瞓底，再咁樣放兩隻手，會容易搵返腹式呼吸<br />\n<br />\n呼吸同把聲好有關係，有氣有聲<br />\n而呢個訓練點都要take time ，如果唔係我學好幾年做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對大家日後咩時候都有幫助，學定無壞！！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">2。Projection</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲唔等於響</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲唔等於響</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲唔等於響</span><br />\n響嘅意思，係將把聲傳到最遠<br />\n大聲，冇呀，企你隔離會聾囉，但啲聲唔會去得遠囉<br />\n係咪好奇怪呢？<br />\n因為講緊聲音係透過空間去傳播<br />\n我哋心入面諗嘅大聲，好容易會出盡奶力<br />\n響，其實係有個意念，將把聲傳出去最遠嘅地方，用岩嘅力！<br />\n點傳呢？<br />\n<br />\n第一樣嘢測試下<br />\n大家坐向張櫈度，試下想像自己痾緊屎，好努力咁必啲屎出嚟！！！<br />\n然後先下講下嘢（普通講嘢得啦）<br />\n應該係好難講到嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你肌肉已經緊晒，鎖實你啲喉嚨！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候夾硬大聲嗌<br />\n你可以farewell 個聲帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發聲要發得響，而唔傷聲，係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用對的肌肉</span></strong><br />\n大家依家試下坐返直，然後將對手，放向你坐緊個個櫈板，然後好似想拎起自己咁提起<br />\n（當然唔會提得起，都唔駛出盡奶力，如果唔係又用錯力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n或者，求其搵兩件重嘢（最好係水桶），左右手各拎一個<br />\n先放鬆，發個長音「啊～～～～～～」，再拎起/提起自己，keep 住個「啊～～～～」<br />\n你應該會發現把聲比平時大左<br />\n唔明？唔緊要！俾埋片你睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OGTjSRVbqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2OGTjSRVbqQ&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ca391221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OGTjSRVbqQ</a><br />\n由9：11 開始睇！<br />\n佢話，想像你腋下有兩舊西瓜，當你要project 個陣，就好似要搾汁出嚟咁<br />\n你會見到佢<span style=\"color: orange;\">好響</span>，而唔係個種<span style=\"color: blue;\">「大聲」</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">3。護聲</span></span></strong><br />\n有正確嘅發聲技巧 <br />\n（其實仲有好多，仲要訓練，係需要時間，但唔緊要，雞精左先）<br />\n就要學點護聲<br />\n如果巴打絲打們已經feel 到自己把聲傷聲<br />\n盡可能，如非必要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好講嘢</span></span><br />\n我哋叫呢啲做vocal rest <br />\n咁如果做老師咁點算...你真係要諗下唔好9嗌得咁大聲<br />\n同埋平時少啲講其他嘢....上網做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，一定要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲水！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n條聲帶要水份，暖水更好<br />\n條聲帶要水份，暖水更好<br />\n條聲帶要水份，暖水更好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">瞓覺！！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n條聲帶要休息<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好食熱氣嘢！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n喉嚨踵左，條聲帶冇咁多位郁會傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結：</span><br />\n講住咁多先<br />\n有朋友叫我拍片，我會睇下幾時有機會拍片<br />\n我估可能我身邊嘅朋友都會拍<br />\n各位要記住，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9嗌唔好真係9嗌</span></span>，真係要錫住把聲<br />\n把聲帶咁勞損，好難修補<br />\n打長久戰，鍚身好重要<br />\n呢啲聲線訓練係需要時間，如果未掌握到，唔緊要<br />\n護住把聲先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要係，大家一齊嗌，咁就唔駛得一個push 把聲架啦！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後最後最後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEqOUyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEqOUyf.jpg&h=2722f546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZwFLyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZwFLyZ.jpg&h=332fe86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打賜教! 小妹已經用緊丹田嗌但都係爛晒聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e095acf94f41f03134efb5bfa09666b26f9808a7","tid":1512603,"uid":300163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60ec119c19e2ee4ea1cc70f67d88836a061b7ec9","tid":1512603,"uid":230803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444d7b55630947998987b19157352cc4e14601fd","tid":1512603,"uid":300163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:04:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好真係9嗌呀屌你</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢派日日落街9嗌，聽到啲手足嗌到把聲沙晒<br />\n我想講，依家係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日日嗌</span></strong></span><br />\n如果唔識得錫住把聲，個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聲帶會好傷</span></strong></span>！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n小弟有做啲啲聲線訓練，唔敢同個啲學opera singing 嘅人比<br />\n但係都可以教到基本嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>發聲</strong></span>、<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">護聲</span></strong>技巧俾大家<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">1。丹田呼吸</span></span></strong><br />\n好啦，見到大家都開post 話丹田呼吸啦<br />\n丹田通常啲人話係肚擠下三個手指位（其實視乎唔同人同學派啦）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">先測試一下你哋平時用咩呼吸方法先！！</span><br />\n各位先坐直，一隻手放向丹田，一隻手放向上胸，然後吸氣<br />\n如果你係上胸姐係漲起先，<br />\n姐係你平時係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">胸口呼吸</span></strong></span><br />\n反之，丹田個隻手漲起，但另一隻手冇漲<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">腹式呼吸</span></span>啦！<br />\n<del>但當然，丹田隻手漲起，再到上胸隻手漲起，又係另一種，學瑜珈太極老師話咁好啲...</del><br />\nAnyway。。。。<br />\n搵到之後，試下得閒就咁做<br />\n吸氣個陣，提自己，丹田個隻手漲起先！要吸氣吸到落丹田！<br />\n仲有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另一個方法</span></strong>，等大家容易啲搵到腹式呼吸<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.jimcdn.com/app/cms/image/transf/dimension=784x10000:format=jpg/path/sd5bb08e12f75bcf7/image/i55d1c4e33781ec9b/version/1471595633/semi-supine-or-constructive-rest-in-the-alexander-technique.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.jimcdn.com%2Fapp%2Fcms%2Fimage%2Ftransf%2Fdimension%3D784x10000%3Aformat%3Djpg%2Fpath%2Fsd5bb08e12f75bcf7%2Fimage%2Fi55d1c4e33781ec9b%2Fversion%2F1471595633%2Fsemi-supine-or-constructive-rest-in-the-alexander-technique.jpg&h=2077ee30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張圖係嚟自Alexander technique 嘅semi supine<br />\n大家試下咁樣瞓底，再咁樣放兩隻手，會容易搵返腹式呼吸<br />\n<br />\n呼吸同把聲好有關係，有氣有聲<br />\n而呢個訓練點都要take time ，如果唔係我學好幾年做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對大家日後咩時候都有幫助，學定無壞！！ <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">2。Projection</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲唔等於響</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲唔等於響</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大聲唔等於響</span><br />\n響嘅意思，係將把聲傳到最遠<br />\n大聲，冇呀，企你隔離會聾囉，但啲聲唔會去得遠囉<br />\n係咪好奇怪呢？<br />\n因為講緊聲音係透過空間去傳播<br />\n我哋心入面諗嘅大聲，好容易會出盡奶力<br />\n響，其實係有個意念，將把聲傳出去最遠嘅地方，用岩嘅力！<br />\n點傳呢？<br />\n<br />\n第一樣嘢測試下<br />\n大家坐向張櫈度，試下想像自己痾緊屎，好努力咁必啲屎出嚟！！！<br />\n然後先下講下嘢（普通講嘢得啦）<br />\n應該係好難講到嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因為你肌肉已經緊晒，鎖實你啲喉嚨！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候夾硬大聲嗌<br />\n你可以farewell 個聲帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發聲要發得響，而唔傷聲，係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">用對的肌肉</span></strong><br />\n大家依家試下坐返直，然後將對手，放向你坐緊個個櫈板，然後好似想拎起自己咁提起<br />\n（當然唔會提得起，都唔駛出盡奶力，如果唔係又用錯力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n或者，求其搵兩件重嘢（最好係水桶），左右手各拎一個<br />\n先放鬆，發個長音「啊～～～～～～」，再拎起/提起自己，keep 住個「啊～～～～」<br />\n你應該會發現把聲比平時大左<br />\n唔明？唔緊要！俾埋片你睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OGTjSRVbqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2OGTjSRVbqQ&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ca391221\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2OGTjSRVbqQ</a><br />\n由9：11 開始睇！<br />\n佢話，想像你腋下有兩舊西瓜，當你要project 個陣，就好似要搾汁出嚟咁<br />\n你會見到佢<span style=\"color: orange;\">好響</span>，而唔係個種<span style=\"color: blue;\">「大聲」</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">3。護聲</span></span></strong><br />\n有正確嘅發聲技巧 <br />\n（其實仲有好多，仲要訓練，係需要時間，但唔緊要，雞精左先）<br />\n就要學點護聲<br />\n如果巴打絲打們已經feel 到自己把聲傷聲<br />\n盡可能，如非必要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好講嘢</span></span><br />\n我哋叫呢啲做vocal rest <br />\n咁如果做老師咁點算...你真係要諗下唔好9嗌得咁大聲<br />\n同埋平時少啲講其他嘢....上網做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，一定要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">飲水！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n條聲帶要水份，暖水更好<br />\n條聲帶要水份，暖水更好<br />\n條聲帶要水份，暖水更好<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">瞓覺！！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n條聲帶要休息<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好食熱氣嘢！！！！！！！！！！！</span></span><br />\n喉嚨踵左，條聲帶冇咁多位郁會傷<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總結：</span><br />\n講住咁多先<br />\n有朋友叫我拍片，我會睇下幾時有機會拍片<br />\n我估可能我身邊嘅朋友都會拍<br />\n各位要記住，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9嗌唔好真係9嗌</span></span>，真係要錫住把聲<br />\n把聲帶咁勞損，好難修補<br />\n打長久戰，鍚身好重要<br />\n呢啲聲線訓練係需要時間，如果未掌握到，唔緊要<br />\n護住把聲先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要係，大家一齊嗌，咁就唔駛得一個push 把聲架啦！！！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後最後最後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEqOUyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEqOUyf.jpg&h=2722f546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PZwFLyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPZwFLyZ.jpg&h=332fe86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打賜教! 小妹已經用緊丹田嗌但都係爛晒聲<img src=